                  <msItem>
                     <p> CHIPPENHAM. Copy in 15th cent. of decree of <persName>
                           <forename>Robert</forename> de  <surname>Brantesim [a mistake for Brantestone?]</surname>, official of <persName>
                              <forename>Robert</forename>, bp. elect of <placeName type="diocese" role="bishop" key="place_107002">Sarum</placeName>
                           </persName>
                        </persName>,
               concerning the appropriation of the church of <placeName key="place_108415">Chippenham</placeName> to the use
               of the <orgName key="org_108111">prior and convent of Farleigh, Wilts</orgName>, and augmenting the vicarage
               with the tithes of <placeName key="place_108618">Tyderington</placeName>, the vicar paying for them 40s. 
               yearly to Farleigh. 
               Dated at <placeName role="date" key="place_107060">Sarum</placeName>, 16 Kl. May, <origDate when="1272">1272</origDate>.
               . </p>
